Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why was it that I was brought back to this world after 3,000 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's because, Dartz, I was brought back in order to defeat you and change the world's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Along with the nameless cards whose seals were broken - the Legendary Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finish off Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! Evil God Gē?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Its Attack Power reached infinity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Infinite Attack Power: Evil God Gē"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear from this realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Special Effect of Legendary Knight Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He absorbs the power of the Monsters from my Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has gained the power of Retrained Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's now protected against Monsters with 1900 Attack Points or greater!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Three Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We bet all on our title!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz. It looks like this is about to be decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time for us to settle this has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gē's Attack Power is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is improbable to surpass that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of their feelings now lie in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Knights! Critias and Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Evil God Gē!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisdom Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What futile effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! There should be no power capable of surpassing that of infinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz, if you believe in the infinity of darkness of the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then the bonds we believe in are {\i1}also{\i0} infinite!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb Attack Guidance Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I add its power to Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the power to send a Monster's attack to another Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the attack will be sent to Hermos instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate the Special Ability of Legendary Knight Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He absorbs three of the Monsters from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He then adds their total Attack Power to his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't have...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! An "infinite loop" was created between the powers of Critias and Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their Attack Points have surpassed Gē's infinite Attack Power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack with Legendary Knight Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Special Ability of Timeaus is to fuse with the Monsters on the field and become an entirely new being!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of our bonds will now open up a brand new future!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gain the power of infinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Dragon Knight - Timeaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch carefully, Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment when the power of bonds overcomes the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've won this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return everyone's souls at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chosen Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to us once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba! Come back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! You really came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jo-Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it back to our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner! Finally... Finally we met again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dartz vanished into the darkness somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then the Legendary Knights revived your souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's still too early to rejoice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my brother's soul returned, then everyone else's souls should also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones who returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others' souls are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Atlantis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means it really exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time to think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive the god Dartz mentioned is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be where all of their souls...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we don't beat that thing, Mai and Varon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amelda's and a ton of other souls as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! The winds have created a tsunami and it's headed right for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the height of the tsunami has already surpassed 100 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will reach America's coastline in approximately one hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we're going to have to go there in order to settle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might be able to get there by helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. I think I know another way we can get there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dimension Dartz vanished into...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be there. I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'm gonna go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that! We just finally managed to get your souls back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma were opponents we couldn't reach to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, you should already know that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we use the power of the Duel Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can stop the Orichalcos God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's right! I'm going to get back Mai and Varon's souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know more than anyone how it feels to be trapped there so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How scary and lonely it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:12:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I always believed that Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} and my other self would rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure the others trapped there are believing that we'll rescue them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we've got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good, Director!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In just one hour, a massive tsunami is going to hit this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My anger won't calm until I settle things with Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell said you could run off on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if some deadbeat could save the glory of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:12:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a minute. I'll switch with my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Stay the Yugi you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you better come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the other Yugi that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better! Yugi! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just wait here and have faith in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...! Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obelisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're finally back with us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the hidden power within these cards has been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure the cards are just happy to be back with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's hurry, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soul cards carved on the wall are all empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that monster eat them all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've got this, I'm even more courageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. This was mine to {\i1}begin{\i0} with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Chosen Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need {\i1}you{\i0} to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really standing in Atlantis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz must be somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz must be up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Dartz's body was already destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were too late, my Chosen Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My God has already been resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! I thought you couldn't revive the God of Orichalcos without our souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed, it is far from complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I shall offer up my soul in your stead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the God of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freakin' {\i1}huge{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sacrificed his own soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Chosen Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one shall be able to stop this God any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth! So that's what the real you looks like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That despicable form?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow me to personally put you out of your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if you {\i0}can{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're gonna just blow us away after we came this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out! Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon's Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Psycho Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gadget Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Vorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, nameless dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend us your powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us your true forms! Legend of Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:19:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the true forms of the Legendary Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, our Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Charged Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Energy Black Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Burst Missile Strike!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use the power of Kuriboh and Multiply and I'll let Timaeus absorb their Landmine Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go, my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone will-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a joke? He wasn't even {\i1}scratched{\i0} after all those attacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a damn minute!\N If that attack hits us...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Knight Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb the abilities of Big Shield Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate his Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wiped all of our Monsters out in one strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on, we'll never win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That light pattern...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:22:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally beat Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But despite that, it looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz used his own soul as the sacrifice and managed to revive the God of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean the Legendary Knights are useless in front of such enormous power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's only a matter of time before the world is submerged by a massive tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Yugi and the guys won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle of the Gods"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
